00:38:33,667 --> 00:38:34,667
I apologize for the ruckus.

554
00:38:38,533 --> 00:38:39,700
Welcome.

555
00:38:40,833 --> 00:38:43,400
I came to thank you
for what you did for my mother.

556
00:38:44,633 --> 00:38:46,667
Your mother?

557
00:38:46,733 --> 00:38:49,733
It seems you mended her lingerie?

558
00:38:50,667 --> 00:38:51,700
Mrs. Ono!

559
00:38:51,767 --> 00:38:52,833
Yes.

560
00:38:52,900 --> 00:38:55,467
Recently, she hasn't been well.

561
00:38:55,533 --> 00:38:57,700
She may have been a nuisance to you.

562
00:38:57,767 --> 00:38:59,067
No, not at all.

563
00:38:59,133 --> 00:39:00,533
Right?

564
00:39:00,600 --> 00:39:02,600
She's very spirited and cheerful.

565
00:39:02,667 --> 00:39:04,467
Thank you so much.

566
00:39:04,533 --> 00:39:06,567
Ever since she came here,

567
00:39:06,633 --> 00:39:08,200
she's suddenly become very lively.

568
00:39:09,433 --> 00:39:11,767
Ma'am, I like this one!

569
00:39:11,833 --> 00:39:13,533
Choose whatever you like.

570
00:39:13,600 --> 00:39:14,767
I'll buy whichever one you like.

571
00:39:14,833 --> 00:39:16,833
Thank you so much, ma'am!

572
00:39:22,167 --> 00:39:23,233
Mrs. Ono!

573
00:39:23,800 --> 00:39:26,633
Women should take care of themselves.

574
00:39:26,700 --> 00:39:28,600
You should wear high quality garments.

575
00:39:29,133 --> 00:39:30,133
Yes.

576
00:39:31,000 --> 00:39:32,067
Thank you.

577
00:39:33,667 --> 00:39:35,767
Welcome, Mrs. Ono.

578
00:39:36,800 --> 00:39:38,333
You...

579
00:39:38,400 --> 00:39:41,567
My bra is now so comfortable,
even under my kimono.

580
00:39:41,633 --> 00:39:43,333
You've been wearing it?

581
00:39:43,400 --> 00:39:44,700
Thank you so much.

582
00:39:44,767 --> 00:39:46,367
Yes, it feels wonderful.

583
00:39:47,333 --> 00:39:48,867
It's incredible,

584
00:39:48,933 --> 00:39:51,367
considering it's 30 years old.

585
00:39:51,433 --> 00:39:54,600
I have better posture when I wear it.

586
00:39:56,800 --> 00:39:59,267
It's as if my husband is telling me

587
00:39:59,333 --> 00:40:01,233
that I need to stand up straight.

588
00:40:03,500 --> 00:40:05,233
Ma'am, look at this one!

589
00:40:06,867 --> 00:40:09,567
Do you think this'll work under a kimono?

590
00:40:10,433 --> 00:40:11,500
I think so.

591
00:40:17,100 --> 00:40:18,767
She wasn't legally married.

592
00:40:19,733 --> 00:40:21,500
She was considered a mistress.

593
00:40:23,067 --> 00:40:26,133
She worked hard as a geisha

594
00:40:26,200 --> 00:40:27,900
and raised me all by herself.

595
00:40:29,133 --> 00:40:32,200
She slowly collected coins in that purse.

596
00:40:36,933 --> 00:40:38,300
It may not seem like much,

597
00:40:38,367 --> 00:40:42,433
but it's her way of expressing gratitude.

598
00:40:48,167 --> 00:40:49,167
I know.

599
00:40:51,367 --> 00:40:52,833
I like that one.

600
00:40:52,900 --> 00:40:54,000
The lace is so pretty.

601
00:40:54,067 --> 00:40:56,133
Yes, it's very pretty.

602
00:41:00,667 --> 00:41:03,200
Eighteen sets all at once!

603
00:41:03,267 --> 00:41:04,733
We did it.

604
00:41:04,800 --> 00:41:06,833
I'm not sure what's going on, but yeah!

605
00:41:06,900 --> 00:41:10,567
But we'll need to purchase
a lot of material.

606
00:41:10,633 --> 00:41:11,800
We need cash, right?

607
00:41:12,933 --> 00:41:14,800
We're going to need cash.

608
00:41:15,733 --> 00:41:18,633
Shall we ask for the payment upfront?

609
00:41:20,267 --> 00:41:21,800
No.

610
00:41:21,867 --> 00:41:23,867
We can't do that.

611
00:41:23,933 --> 00:41:26,467
I could pay out of my own pocket.

612
00:41:26,533 --> 00:41:28,933
Why don't you hand over your paycheck?

613
00:41:29,000 --> 00:41:31,833
Now that Sosuke quit,
why are you still here?

614
00:41:31,900 --> 00:41:34,233
You guys only pay for my travel expenses.

615
00:41:35,100 --> 00:41:37,667
I don't quite have
the financial means yet.

616
00:41:43,800 --> 00:41:45,733
Where did you get all this?

617
00:41:45,800 --> 00:41:47,167
I borrowed from my ex-girlfriends.

618
00:41:48,867 --> 00:41:50,667
There's about five of them?

619
00:41:50,733 --> 00:41:53,400
Women have a soft spot
for men who are in trouble.

620
00:41:57,100 --> 00:41:58,900
If we can get through this,

621
00:41:58,967 --> 00:42:00,967
Emotion will make it.

622
00:42:14,067 --> 00:42:15,967
It's not much.

623
00:42:16,033 --> 00:42:17,133
But please, use it.

624
00:42:18,033 --> 00:42:20,300
Otherwise, I couldn't forgive myself.

625
00:42:21,867 --> 00:42:24,100
I allowed Hime to make the sacrifice.

626
00:42:50,567 --> 00:42:51,800
It's heavy.

627
00:42:55,567 --> 00:42:57,167
It must be the weight

628
00:42:58,733 --> 00:43:01,133
of the pride you had to set aside.

629
00:43:15,333 --> 00:43:16,600
He must have been so frustrated.

630
00:43:18,133 --> 00:43:19,133
Saru.

631
00:43:22,700 --> 00:43:24,633
It was my fault.

632
00:43:25,600 --> 00:43:28,333
Business isn't always pretty.

633
00:43:30,733 --> 00:43:34,000
I thought I could just make and sell

634
00:43:34,067 --> 00:43:35,933
whatever I wanted to.

635
00:43:39,133 --> 00:43:44,000
Perhaps I was the presumptuous one.

636
00:44:04,467 --> 00:44:05,800
What, you're still here?

637
00:44:06,700 --> 00:44:07,700
Yes.

638
00:44:11,033 --> 00:44:12,133
What?

639
00:44:12,200 --> 00:44:13,233
Why are you standing there?

640
00:44:14,833 --> 00:44:16,067
I'm very sorry.

641
00:44:17,867 --> 00:44:19,233
For what?

642
00:44:21,633 --> 00:44:23,333
For saying you were just looking away.

643
00:44:27,333 --> 00:44:30,533
For telling you to
just express your feelings.

644
00:44:31,700 --> 00:44:32,967
It was stupid of me.

645
00:44:36,400 --> 00:44:37,400
I'm sorry.

646
00:44:37,467 --> 00:44:38,667
Don't apologize!

647
00:44:44,367 --> 00:44:45,767
Don't apologize.

648
00:44:47,900 --> 00:44:49,667
I'm the one who encouraged him.

649
00:44:50,667 --> 00:44:51,700
Fujimura.

650
00:44:53,967 --> 00:44:55,300
It's now my responsibility

651
00:44:56,633 --> 00:44:58,167
to make things right.

652
00:45:10,567 --> 00:45:12,367
Yes, thank you.

653
00:45:12,433 --> 00:45:14,500
We look forward to it.

654
00:45:17,567 --> 00:45:19,367
-I'm heading out.
-See you later.

655
00:45:23,133 --> 00:45:26,100
Reiko, is the order form
for Ms. Hashimoto ready?

656
00:45:26,167 --> 00:45:28,867
Yes, it's ready to go.

657
00:45:29,733 --> 00:45:30,967
ORDER FORM

658
00:45:31,033 --> 00:45:33,400
Lace with glitter.

659
00:45:33,467 --> 00:45:34,867
Did we have that in stock?

660
00:45:36,467 --> 00:45:38,067
It's later than I thought.

661
00:45:48,967 --> 00:45:50,333
Hello?

662
00:45:52,567 --> 00:45:53,567
Welcome.

663
00:45:56,367 --> 00:46:00,467
I figured it's been too long
since I had something made.

664
00:46:01,500 --> 00:46:02,667
I'm so glad.

665
00:46:02,767 --> 00:46:04,767
Thank you for stopping by!

666
00:46:20,700 --> 00:46:22,500
Thank you so much!

667
00:46:30,033 --> 00:46:31,833
Sorry. I didn't hear you.

668
00:46:32,733 --> 00:46:33,733
What is it?

669
00:46:35,067 --> 00:46:36,967
I'd like to try again.

670
00:46:40,800 --> 00:46:44,867
I want more people to know about Emotion.

671
00:46:49,500 --> 00:46:53,733
Will you let me work on
another second line?

672
00:49:17,567 --> 00:49:22,067
{\an8}THIS IS A WORK OF FICTION.

